				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I've been chipping away at my dev setup/framework, <a href="https://github.com/Optiroc/libSFX" class="postlink">libSFX</a>, for some time now. It started life to handle S-CPU boilerplate for my S-APU tinkering (and to get me out of the tools ghetto that this thread is mostly about), but now it's possibly a good starting point for anyone that wants to get started with some SNES coding.</div>

